# CubeOS Workspace
This is the root directory for the CubeOS project, containing shared libraries and services for the Cube-OS Linux ecosystem.

## Structure
- `libs/cubeos-core`: Shared library for CubeOS components.
- `services/cubeos-app`: Application crate for CubeOS apps.
- `services/cubeos-service`: Service crate for CubeOS services.

## Building
Run `cargo build` in this directory to build all crates in the workspace.